OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start in the
OL,6,Fwest and Ayrshire but cloudier in the
OL,7,Feast with some outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Fwintry on higher ground. Drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter for a time in the afternoon.
OL,10,FMostly light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClouding over in the evening
OL,13,Fwith some rain spreading east and
OL,14,Ffreshening southwesterly winds, drier
OL,15,Ffor a time but further rain by dawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA wet and windy start on
OL,18,FSunday rain quite persistent for
OL,19,FAyrshire but brighter for a time
OL,20,Felsewhere, further rain by evening and
OL,21,Fquite blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
