OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA wet
OL,6,Fstart for the beginning of the new
OL,7,Fweek but becoming drier and brighter
OL,8,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday with plenty
OL,9,Fof March sunshine.
